name: dpmcmlxxvi
body:
### [Current repositories](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi)

Name  | Description
----- | -------------
[clistats](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/clistats) | A C++ application to compute statistics for a stream of input numbers.
[clitestbed](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/clitestbed) | A C++ application test bed to run a suite of tests on a program.
[olexp](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/olexp) | A Javascript library that combines OpenLayers with a layout manager.
[pixelscan](https://github.com/dpmcmlxxvi/pixelscan) | A Python library to scan pixels on a grid in a variety of spatial patterns.
